  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Wendel</b> and <b>Wendell</b> are given names in Westeros and may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Frey\" title=\"Wendel Frey\">Wendel Frey</a>, a son of Walder Frey and his seventh wife Annara Farring</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Manderly\" title=\"Wendel Manderly\">Wendel Manderly</a>, the second son of Wyman Manderly</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wendell_Webber\" title=\"Wendell Webber\">Wendell Webber</a>, a knight of House Webber during the reign of King Aerys I</li>\n<li>Wendel, a member of the Night's Watch in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_A_Telltale_Games_Series\" title=\"Game of Thrones - A Telltale Games Series\">Game of Thrones - A Telltale Games Series</a></i></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405045541\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.002 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:31801-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405045541 and revision id 332117\n -->\n",
